\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{VR}*\boldsymbol{h}_{P}=(\boldsymbol{V}-\boldsymbol{\beta}\sigma_{B}^{2}\boldsymbol{\beta}^{T})\boldsymbol{h}_{P}=\boldsymbol{V}\boldsymbol{h}_{P}-\frac{\boldsymbol{V}\boldsymbol{h}_{B}}{\sigma_{B}^{2}}\sigma_{B}^{2}\beta_{P}=\boldsymbol{V}(\boldsymbol{h}_{P}-\beta_{P}\boldsymbol{h}_{B})$
\end_inset


\end_layout

