\begin_inset Formula $k_{1}=\frac{\beta_{PA}*\sigma_{B}^{2}}{\psi_{P}}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $k_{2}=\frac{\omega_{P}}{\psi_{P}}$
\end_inset

。【
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\beta}*k_{1}=\boldsymbol{\beta}*\sigma_{B}^{2}*\boldsymbol{\beta}^{T}\boldsymbol{h}_{PA}*\frac{1}{\psi_{P}}=(\boldsymbol{V}-\boldsymbol{VR})\frac{\boldsymbol{h}_{PA}}{\psi_{P}}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{MCRR}*k_{2}=\frac{\boldsymbol{VR}*\boldsymbol{h}_{P}}{\psi_{P}}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{VR}*\boldsymbol{h}_{B}=\mathbf{0}$
\end_inset

】。可以看出，
\begin_inset Formula $0\leq k_{2}\leq1$
\end_inset

，并且当
\begin_inset Formula $\beta_{PA}=0$
