附录
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
首先，将组合持仓权重
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{h}_{P}$
\end_inset

、超额收益率预测
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}$
\end_inset

和组合方差
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{P}^{2}$
\end_inset

分别分解为业绩基准部分和关于该业绩基准的残差部分。
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{h}_{PR}$
\end_inset

代表组合P在风险资产上的残差头寸，于是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boldsymbol{h}_{P}=\beta_{P}\boldsymbol{h}_{B}+\boldsymbol{h}_{PR}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{P}=\beta_{P}f_{B}+\alpha_{P}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{P}^{2}=\beta_{P}^{2}\sigma_{B}^{2}+\omega_{P}^{2}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $\beta_{P}=\frac{Cov\{r_{P},r_{B}\}}{Var\{r_{B}\}}$
\end_inset

，于是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
f_{P} & =f_{B}+\beta_{PA}f_{B}+\alpha_{P}\\
 & =f_{B}+\beta_{PA}\mu_{B}+\beta_{PA}\Delta f_{B}+\alpha_{P}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma_{P}^{2} & =(1+\beta_{PA})^{2}\sigma_{B}^{2}+\omega_{P}^{2}\\
 & =\sigma_{B}^{2}+2\beta_{PA}\sigma_{B}^{2}+\beta_{PA}^{2}\sigma_{B}^{2}+\omega_{P}^{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

效用函数的一般形式为
\begin_inset Formula $u=f-\lambda\sigma^{2}$
\end_inset

，于是，我们将
\begin_inset Formula $f_{P}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{P}^{2}$
\end_inset

分解的各项对应起来，并代入效用函数，就可以得到由下述四项构成的整体效用函数：
\end_layout

